      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="Wienbibliothek_AS_FS_2823304"/><salute>lieber Salten,</salute> bitte ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en Sie <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03034-1"/><date when="1898-01-28">morgen Freitag</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03034-1">Dadurch ist das Korrespondenzstück
                  datierbar, <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1898-01-28" subtype="cf"/>.</note><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>8 Uhr</time> zum Nachtmahl <pb facs="Wienbibliothek_AS_FS_2823305"/>zu uns
                  <add place="inline">(<rs type="person" ref="#pmb10992">Brandes</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="latintype">etc.</hi>)</add></p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <lb/>Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
